country_additional: Also in Mozambique, Nicaragua, Nigeria, Swaziland, Tanzania and Zambia. IMPORTANT NOTE: Scope of Contract: This is NOT a construction contract. The contract is predominantly for health commodity procurement. Renovation of warehouses is necessary to safeguard stock and ensure they are well racked, secured and stored in temperature controlled environment. All the renovation works under this contract were applied to already existing structures. Renovation is limited to racking, shelving, installation of A/C, installation of security systems, management information systems, and other interior improvements. NO work was done that changed the footprint of a building OR the outside awnings, raising roofs, outside ramp changes, outside paved walkways, anything to do with concrete (including demolition of concrete), drains that require digging or drilling, and/or foundation for drains and fencing. Pre-Fabricated Structures: We have procured turn-key pre-fabricated warehouses and clinics. Pre-fabs are installed on flat concrete slabs constructed by Host Governments, which include all pre-installed utility work (power, water, drains, etc.)
